Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个事件已经过去一个多月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们家还继续住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到我是「蜜」的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想还是尽早离开比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但眠同学说多亏天气逐渐变凉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不会有之前那样的影响了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以打算暂时再多留一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要更深地理解这个镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在将来把此事正确地传达给社会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲已经开始着手干了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看他那个样子  该做的时候还是会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.48,0:00:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好湿…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除社会对神人的偏见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说只是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.76,0:01:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既然我已经来到了这个镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这是我被赋予的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次由我来保护小铃和眠同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.21,0:01:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…有点太耍帅了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃  眠同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博还是老样子那么夸张呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.72,0:01:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在想些H的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  今天是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧  小要在等我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让我们「神秘现象探究会」正式作为社团被认可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  要同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也算进去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？没有听小铃说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果提前告诉小博的话肯定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中时也没参加什么社团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是归家部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样那样说  肯定会拒绝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就说和我们来一下  于是就带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事！我什么都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的感觉  完全不清楚今天开会的主旨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个人有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人头疼呢  明明也是部员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…我还没说要加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…神秘现象…研究会来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探究会！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  眠同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  的确
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究  也就是用知识对某事物的考察  实验和观察
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔还会需要调查  来追究事物的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面  探究是为了获得某事物而对其寻求  最后获得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如要同学所说  意义上是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗  博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  为了让学校认同「神秘现象探究会」这个社团
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和眠同学还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁喉技…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能输  好好干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么恶搞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家太没干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…果然我也被算上了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体要做些什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说探究这种神秘生物的存在之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  之前就想问了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠  那个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔耳青蛙先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔耳青蛙先生？那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔耳青蛙先生也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去买点喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说小博
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博真是的  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦和眠同学说到兔耳青蛙先生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会发生很可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠同…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  有客人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兔耳青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎  眠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  刚才的那是小眠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然眠的兔耳青蛙的问候好神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专业的兔耳青蛙粉丝的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的问候是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是眠  真让人陶醉崇拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的主题是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:08:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  今天打算两个人一起考虑兔耳青蛙先生的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔耳青蛙先生…的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人想的话一定能描绘出很棒的家的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想  说到兔耳青蛙先生的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然应该是豪华的城堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔耳青蛙女王和许多的仆人一起居住着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王…和仆人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那可能也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈喜欢这样的倒是有点意外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我倒认为很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市的孩子都那么追求刺激吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外在城堡里还要建一个宽广的庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在那里养着小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩猎…狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做的话  反而会被狗狩猎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想到如此可怕的设定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市的孩子果然是在追求刺激…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  真是不错的设定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想一起住在那样的城堡里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起住？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会每天都很欢乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然那样笑着说这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄麻奈  可怕的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个梦想  让我帮你实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要建造兔耳青蛙的城堡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  这可是为了重要的兔耳伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么事不宜迟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔  丰收  检索  漫步  创作  搜索  结果还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔  丰收  检索  漫步  创作  搜索  结果还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔  丰收  检索  漫步  创作  搜索  结果还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…猎户大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然要解除我们一族流传的禁忌咒术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…麻奈的话已经睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  那么请把这个交给麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给麻奈就会明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外麻奈以外的人千万不要打开箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都这么说了  我就稍微看下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  发生过这样的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真是太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小博  你脖子那里被什么东西咬了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然嫦娥的八朔果汁最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧  我也最喜欢果汁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来之前真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个电视台的取材
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是脏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就想起了那打算永远丢弃的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问需要些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是来找今天在这里打工的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来点冰咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美味哦  冰咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这个…我是被朋友叫来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糖汁甜甜的…甜甜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏糊糊…黏糊糊…拉着丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰咖啡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰咖啡  明明那么好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  我的服务生打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个啊  是眠同学让我随身带着防身用的八朔喷剂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  就那么没信用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不带也没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…说不定会有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  为什么突然开始打工了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了不要惊讶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实今天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫦娥有线电视
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来这家店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博真是冷静过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个「早安嫦娥」节目组要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是有线电视吗  不用这么兴奋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢  博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「早安嫦娥」可是收视率70%的怪谈节目哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是因为这样才会被别人说成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「存在微薄的眼镜男」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「除气味以外都中等以下」之类的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分…不过这样的咖啡店电视台来取什么材
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这家店偶尔会出现的  那个神秘的服务生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的服务生？那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  传闻的话听过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是不管对方是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切让人困扰的客人都会赶走的传说人物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称「嫦娥之重」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「嫦娥之重」？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎样的人呢  快点来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  我该做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  小博好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃快说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了我还什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细小的事就别在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多神秘的服务生就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  眠同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠一定是想上电视才来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶尔也会来咖啡店的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神人耳朵很好使呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…请问需要些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生鱼片海苔寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…牛舌鱼的法国式黄油烤鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便来一份猪肉饭  尽可能小份的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠是第一次来咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是很想上电视呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢  萨布  听说今天电视台要来这家店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之来点啤酒  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下酒菜就来点毛豆和酱黄瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨布
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到酱黄瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有热恋的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了小姐  请和我结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要拒绝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看大哥这样  好歹也算是一个地痞流氓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨布  别这样夸奖嘛  会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  小博他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底有什么魅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是被博士君的「蜜」所吸引…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来进行落神之式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  你的气味真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想亲一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥你太大胆了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好  就一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候神秘的服务生能来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了  客人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能允许你继续无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮客人点菜15年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算上收银20年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称  神秘的服务生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「嫦娥之重」就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「嫦娥之重」那是什么？大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这呆子  不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前本打算抢下这个镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个在日本也是屈指可数的的黑道「关东碑与虎组」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他仅仅一人就赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  那个碑与虎组吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「嫦娥之重」…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是眠同学的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说了还不听劝的话那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堕落之神  挥之除去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(303,434)\fs24}狼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下不妙了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  真的赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲  真是漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  眠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一件事要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天本来预订要进行「早安嫦娥」的取材
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以替我电话通知电视台  说我希望能中止吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我腰扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠啊  之后的就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果那个电视台的企画取消了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是挺有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博的服务生打扮也很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说别再让我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  干脆就组一个「Cosplay探究会」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都让小博穿可爱的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠也喜欢Cosplay什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…还好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔耳青蛙先生的人偶装的话我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起扮成兔耳青蛙的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
