Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:53.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱之彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:59.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}接连着伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:12.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心口难开 「君莫泣」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:18.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}渐次斑驳  世界之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:25.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}身在旅途　至终焉之河
