Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:35.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如日削月割
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:47.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}故乡迢迢  时之彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:50.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}与君共往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:53.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无爱无心
